3D PRINTING IN SPACE: Join us to meet Made In Space's team, and learn about Archinaut One from the people leading the project, 3D printing satellites in space. Interested in the business opportunities and engineering challenges of the final frontier? New Space at Berkeley is bringing you industry leaders to discuss careers of the future, right now.

Join via Zoom on your own, or come to Sibley Auditorium for Made in Space Swag and hybrid-panel!

When: 9/30 2:00-3:00 PM 

Zoom Link: https://berkeley.zoom.us/j/96771608216?pwd=Smo5Mmx0UFFtbTlZcDVOdk1YT29YQT09

RSVP here: https://forms.gle/mWxvu9XLH1jdgooYA
